high_descs: Take a step left and walk to the end of the counter on the left.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn right and walk all the way to the wall, then turn left to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge in front of the bowl. Close the door, wait a moment, and then take it out again.
Turn left and take a few steps, then turn left and go to the counter with the toaster on it.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a counter.

high_descs: Go left and stop in front of the counter where the lettuce is.
Pick the lettuce up from the counter.
Go right and turn left to face the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the lettuce out and shut the door.
Go left and then left again to face the counter to the left of the toaster.
Put the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Move over to the lettuce on the counter, left of the sink.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right, bring the lettuce down to the fridge past the sink on the left.
Chill the lettuce in the sink.
Bring the chilled lettuce to the counter with the toaster and coffee machine, which is on the other side of the room as the sink.
Put the chilled lettuce on the counter near the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the counter.
